channel.title: Trouble with Breaks
channel.description: I think aryan is taking too many breaks... it logs out but the script relogs in and then it keeps repeating. i edited the breaks file but nothing happened. anyone else get this?

item.title: Trouble with Breaks
item.dc:creator: @yeha_x_d yeha x d
item.description:
@yeha_x_d wrote:

unless the command promt window says that its having a break your not having one…

what your describing sounds more like you have a very laggy internet connection…your connection dies the client logs out…the autoer logs in because its programmed to automatically (duh)…if your internet still sucks cock he lags out again

if you have other things on the internet then get rid of them…also get a better connection speed
